&lt;li&gt;In partnership with the VP of Sales and the Chief Growth Officer, manage the sales cycle, including outreach, stakeholder alignment, partnership terms negotiation, and agreement finalization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain a deep understanding of Belong Health&#39;s solutions, including the technology and services offered, to effectively communicate value propositions to potential partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain industry leading expertise around Medicare programs, Special Needs Plans, and value-based care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze market dynamics (competitive, network, utilization) to uncover key insights for prospects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal teams, such as Analytics, Product, and Operations to gather relevant data and insights to support business development efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Belong Health at relevant industry conferences and events and participate in professional organizations to generate interest and build relationships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create sales collateral, presentations, and other marketing materials to support the Growth team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
